<ab facs="#facs_98_r1l5">fürſten / . <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> gnedigiſten <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> ~ des <expan>Romiſch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc künigs </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_98_r1l6">gnaden geweſen ſein . Alſo iſt vns von <expan>deſſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> </ab>
